{"tid":776272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑容太犯規！日本最可愛高一女孩出爐","createTime":"2018-08-12T01:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T05:37:14.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0540067e6a81884a0678317c77676c9827fb52a2","tid":776272,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:54:09.000Z","msg":"日本一年一度「最可愛高一女學生」選美比賽結果終於出爐，新科冠軍由來自靜岡縣的刑部結生奪下，擁有一頭飄逸長髮得她，加上可愛又甜美燦笑，讓一向毒舌的日本網友無可挑剔，甚至大讚「太犯規！」<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/26NXYa.2i57z9IYvJ15Gsw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/121255c49458f2febe7ea3a5f461c9a9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F26NXYa.2i57z9IYvJ15Gsw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F121255c49458f2febe7ea3a5f461c9a9&h=57f493ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲刑部結生燦笑令酸民都戀愛了。（圖／翻攝自mdpr）<br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，日本2018年最可「愛高一女學生」選美比賽結果於9日出爐，16歲來自靜岡縣的刑部結生，靠著可愛甜美的笑容，擊敗千名對手拿下今年冠軍，喜歡吃麵包的她，原本立志要開麵包店，不過現在她也開始思考是否進入演藝圈的可能，甚至不排斥成為一名專業模特兒。<br />\n檢視相片<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nF6DJ2jbC_RQHot6VI_t9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/5ceb32cfae04a2e6f5cb8374938b82a7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnF6DJ2jbC_RQHot6VI_t9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9Mjg3%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F5ceb32cfae04a2e6f5cb8374938b82a7&h=f69c336a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲擁有偶像基因的上水口姬香榮獲亞軍。（圖／翻攝自mdpr）<br />\n<br />\n亞軍則由擁有一雙水汪汪大眼睛，國中開時就以偶像身分從事活動的上水口姬香榮得，更令人值得一提的是，上水口姬香的姊姊就是日本知名歌手上水口萌乃香，可說本身就擁有著偶像的基因，雖然只獲得亞軍仍是實至名歸。"},{"pid":"f53ca8eb6fd4baec1d59ac70ab68b20694a37456","tid":776272,"uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"亞軍有d樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1a07948de2ad08f5c77cfffb669b1f1667a434","tid":776272,"uid":19557,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"冠軍實至名歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35eeee81441c048ba6e6bfeb50e80965c4cba01e","tid":776272,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:59:45.000Z","msg":"淨係童童都贏曬佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acedecab989bca6eab96afda6e6be58e7942ab5b","tid":776272,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"日本16歲樣唔錯既性經驗人數應該已經超過10個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601d76f891946c315485017406de4549e94ab663","tid":776272,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為可愛加上毒舌<br />\n咁就無敵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9a82f1ede1a3f8bf30999d031a6b0247e546b2","tid":776272,"uid":71864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:05:58.000Z","msg":"支持上水人"},{"pid":"9106fee99b03a86f8e64bbda403eaf509c7d4801","tid":776272,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"acedecab989bca6eab96afda6e6be58e7942ab5b","tid":776272,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"日本16歲樣唔錯既性經驗人數應該已經超過10個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:07:44.000Z","msg":"ching我offtopic 但好似去親咩post都見到你咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794c2f724fef2e04a25675af8bbb04919fd059d